@page "/About"

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-9 col-xl-8">
            <article class="prose">
                <header class="mb-4 text-center">
                    <h1 class="display-6 fw-semibold">About The Bloggest</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted">Our purpose, mission, and the story behind it.</p>
                </header>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="h4">Purpose</h2>
                    <p>
                        TheBloggest is a modern blogging platform built to empower writers, share stories, and connect communities.
                        Whether you’re a seasoned author or hitting publish for the first time, we make it delightful to write,
                        read, and discover ideas that matter.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="h4">Mission</h2>
                    <p>
                        Our mission is to lower the barrier to publishing, encourage thoughtful conversations, and provide a clean,
                        fast, and accessible reading experience on every device.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="h4">Vision</h2>
                    <p>
                        We envision a vibrant, open community where creators own their voice, readers find meaningful content,
                        and great ideas travel further with the help of simple, well-crafted tools.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="h4">Inspiration</h2>
                    <p>
                        TheBloggest was inspired by classic web publishing, thoughtful newsletters, and the elegance of minimalist
                        design. We believe in clarity over clutter, substance over noise, and giving creators room to breathe.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>